[[欧洲科学与艺术学院|欧洲科学与艺术学院]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.euro-acad.eu/members |title=Members of the European Academy of Sciences and Arts |accessdate=2015-02-14 |archive-date=2015-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222151927/http://www.euro-acad.eu/members |dead-url=yes }}</ref> ，[[欧洲分子生物协会|欧洲分子生物协会]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.embo.org/embo-members.html |title=Members of the EMBO |access-date=2015-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116063728/http://embo.org/embo-members.html |archive-date=2013-01-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> ，以及[[柏林布兰登堡科学与人文科学院|柏林布兰登堡科学与人文科学院]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbaw.de/die-akademie/mitglieder |title=Members of the Berlin-Brandenburgische Akademie der Wissenschaften |access-date=2015-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302130002/http://www.bbaw.de/die-akademie/mitglieder |archive-date=2015-03-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；并受到多个组织嘉奖。他获得重要的奖项包括 Carus Prize（[[德国利奥波第那科学院|德国利奥波第那科学院]]，2009年）<ref>[http://www.leopoldina.org/de/akademie/preise-und-auszeichnungen/carus-medaille.html Germany Academy of Sciences Leopoldina, list of Carus Medal recipients] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723062308/http://www.leopoldina.org/de/akademie/preise-und-auszeichnungen/carus-medaille.html |date=2011-07-23 }}</ref>,  EMBO Award for Communication in Life Science（欧洲分子生物学组织，2008年）<ref>"[http://www.embo.org/documents/press08/communications_award08.pdf Prominent German biologist wins EMBO communication award.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722091616/http://www.embo.org/documents/press08/communications_award08.pdf |date=2011-07-22 }}" European Molecular Biology Organization, press release.</ref>, [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guggenheim_Fellowship|John Simon Guggenheim Memorial Fellowship]{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} (1996年)<ref>[[List_of_Guggenheim_Fellowships_awarded_in_1996|List of Guggenheim Fellowships awarded in 1996]]</ref><ref>[htt